  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 53bfd23aa9861cb42a751716744564d2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Intro Bill 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  line: It's big, Harvey. The biggest gathering we've seen yet. All three families
    under the same roof. It's too big to ignore. Some kinda poker tournament they're
    running, we don't know what for. We bummed the invite off one of the Marino goons
    we caught in the raid, that's you. Keep your head down and no one will know you
    don't belong.
  speakerName: Bill
